snippet.title: [Devil May Cry: Peak of Combat] Lady gameplay teaser
snippet.description:
Hunters can now PRE-REGISTER using Email on the official website for the chance to participate in the Closed Beta Test and get guaranteed rewards in Open Beta.

Official website: http://dmcen.nebulajoy.com/landingpage.html

Stay updated by following: 
🔵Twitter: https://twitter.com/dmc_poc
🔵Facebook: http://facebook.com/gaming/DevilMayCryPeakofCombat
🔴YouTube: http://youtube.com/@devilmaycrypeakofcombat
Don't forget to join our Demon Hunter Legion on the official Discord Server
🟣Discord: http://discord.gg/vBWSvK9n6m
